                            <h3>Edgar - Fill Green</h3>
                            <p>Edgar is an eco-friendly foodie offering food in bulk and sustainable lifestyle products.</p>
                        </div>
                </div>
                <div class="item">
                        <figure class="cover">
                                <img style="padding-top: 20px; "src="https://whub-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/logo/file/5371f2193832390002090000/large_screen-2.png">
